      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All constructs manufactured to production drawing revision C. Dimensional inspection reports confirm geometric conformance. Sample size exceeds minimum requirement."
    },
    {
