      "acceptanceCriteria": "Simulation input parameters (geometry, material, boundary conditions) must be demonstrably equivalent to experimental conditions; any discrepancies must be quantified and their effect on QoI assessed.",
      "rationale": "Simulation geometry derived from CAD nominal with dimensional inspection overlay confirming <0.05 mm deviation. Boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture kinematics. Torque applied to set screws in simulation matches experimental protocol (4 Nm). Equivalency confirmed; residual geometric discrepancy contributes <1% to QoI uncertainty."
    },
