      "rationale": "E/uval computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 9 for all three QoIs: stiffness E/uval=0.87, yield force E/uval=1.21, force at 40 mm E/uval=1.55. All values below 1.96 threshold. Comparison metric satisfies acceptance criterion at Gradation 3."
